  "description": "<p><strong>其实现在柔性可弯曲显示屏已经不是什么新鲜事儿了，之前有索尼公司推出的E-Ink柔性显示屏产品可用作教育使用，而最近E-Ink公司的项目经理 Giovanni Mancini向外媒CNET展示了公司即会推广到Kindle，Nook和索尼Reader上的新电子墨水显示技术。</strong>首先新技术改善减少了在翻页后依然残留部分文字的重影现象，这样用户就不需要频繁的进行刷新操作。目前的设备往往翻六七页之后就需要进行一次刷新，而新技术有望达到100页。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ea6c4e7/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244647.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0E-Ink%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%8FKindle%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%AE%E4%B8%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244647.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0E-Ink%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%8FKindle%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%AE%E4%B8%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244647.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0E-Ink%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%8FKindle%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%AE%E4%B8%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244647.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A0E-Ink%E6%9F%94%E6%80%A7%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%A8%E6%B0%B4%E5%B1%8FKindle%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%AE%E4%B8%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244647.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%A