  "date": "Sun, 14 Jul 2013 23:43:27 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244646.htm", 
  "description": "<p>如果你正在期待一款采用所谓的“视网膜”显示屏的iPad mini，你最好还是把这种期待推迟到下一个季度。因为据推测，iPad mini 2将采用与现在的iPad mini一样的显示屏。原因有两点，<strong>一是自从iPad 2推出以来，iPad的显示屏分辨率就一直未曾提高，这说明iPad高端的显示技术已经达到极限。另外，现在的电子产品普遍遵循一个规律，那就是新的智能 手机和平板将不会比前一代的产品高端很多，这样大众会比较容易接受新的产品。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ea6c4e6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244646.htm&amp;t=%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0iPad+mini+2%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244646.htm&amp;t=%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0iPad+mini+2%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244646.htm&amp;t=%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0iPad+mini+2%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244646.htm&amp;t=%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0iPad+mini+2%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8%E2%80%9C%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E2%80%9D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Fa